# Environment variables for LOCAL k6 tests.
# -----------------------------------------
# To use, create a file named '.env' in this same directory (tests-k6/local/.env)
# and add your local JWT token to it.

# How to get the token:
# 1. Run the application locally with `docker compose up`.
# 2. Log in at http://localhost using your Google account.
# 3. Open your browser's developer tools (F12).
# 4. Go to the "Application" tab -> "Local Storage" -> click on "http://localhost".
# 5. Copy the long string value from the 'token' key.

AUTH_TOKEN="YOUR_LOCAL_JWT_TOKEN_HERE"